<DOCID> 061271 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
July 17, 1994, Sunday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
TV Times; Page 4; Television Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
