<HEADLINE>
<P>
SIGN OF THE TIMES 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 "Weird Androgynous Sign" is too long, and "TAFKAP" sounds like an obscure 
military procurement program (Letters, July 3). 
</P>
<P>
 Regardless, both are unnecessary. As any student of hieroglyphics knows, the 
symbol by which that silly Minneapolis-based publicity scarfer wants to be 
known is pronounced "Doofus." 
</P>
<P>
 Can we all shut up and go home now? 
</P>
<P>
 ANDREW SUSSMAN 
</P>
<P>
 Rancho Santa Margarita 
</P>
