<P>
 In addition to the usual table-hopping that occurs at the Grill at lunchtime, 
the place virtually looked like a game of musical chairs on Monday. 
</P>
<P>
 Even among this hard-to-impress crowd, the ogle-level went up several notches 
when O.J. Simpson's defense team of Robert Shapiro, Gerald Uelmen and Alan 
Dershowitz took a booth. Seated at another table: Robert Kardashian. 
</P>
