<HEADLINE>
<P>
NEWS, TIPS & BARGAINS; PLACES FOR INNER JOURNEYS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 If you yearn to see new places but also travel inward, the latest edition of 
U.S. and Worldwide Guide to Retreat Center Guest Houses lists more than 740 
guest houses in the U.S., Canada, Europe, New Zealand and Australia.Forty-nine 
are in the United States. 
</P>
<P>
 Retreat Centers are church-affiliated centers that offer refuge and 
accommodations to guests of any religious persuasion -- or none at all. Rates 
usually run about $30-$40 a day, including meals. 
</P>
<P>
 The guide is $15.95 and available from CTS Publications, P.O. Box 8355, 
Newport Beach, Calif. 92660. First-class postage is $2. 
