<DOCID> 061409 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
July 17, 1994, Sunday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Metro; Part B; Page 9; Column 1; Metro Desk 
</P>
