<P>
A NEW HATE CRIME 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 * Re: "Waging Personal War Against Bigotry" (July 3): Brian Levin is on the 
right trail, working for increased sentencing for the hate crimes. 
</P>
<P>
 Now if he would work to classify AIDS transmission by HIV-infected individuals 
as hate crime, we would be getting somewhere. 
</P>
<P>
 Transmission of AIDS is a death sentence against another human being. You 
can't get much more hateful than that. 
</P>
<P>
 H.R. CLARKE 
</P>
<P>
 Laguna Beach 
</P>
