<P>
 This school year City Times has honored the best on the playing fields. This 
week, we pay tribute to the high school valedictorians from the Central City. 
</P>
<P>
 The outstanding students were asked: "What kind of future does Los Angeles 
hold for you and your classmates?" 
</P>
