<P>
BAILEY A. THOMAS; MCCORMICK SPICE COMPANY CHAIRMAN 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Bailey A. Thomas, 63, chairman and chief executive officer of McCormick & 
Co.He joined the spice and seasonings company in 1961 and had been a director 
since 1977. He was named president and chief executive officer in March, 1992, 
and became chairman and CEO on Jan. 1, 1993. President and chief operating 
officer H. Eugene Blattman will head the company until the board of directors 
chooses a successor, probably in the next few days. McCormick, based in Sparks, 
Nev., has 8,600 employees worldwide. In Sparks on Thursday of a heart attack. 
