<HEADLINE>
<P>
HORACE COLLINS; HBO VICE PRESIDENT AND LEGAL COUNSEL 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Horace Collins, 44, senior vice president and assistant general counsel of 
Home Box Office.Collins oversaw all legal aspects of HBO's feature film 
financing, licensing, programming and distribution. He also headed the cable 
network's West Coast programming, including production of films and specials. 
When based in Los Angeles, he served on the board of the Los Angeles Gay and 
Lesbian Community Services Center and was active with the Gay and Lesbian 
Alliance Against Defamation. In New York City on Wednesday of the complications 
of AIDS. 
