<HEADLINE>
<P>
THANKS TO THOSE WHO REBUILT THE FREEWAYS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Thanks to the many workers who spent much energy and time away from their 
families to rebuild the Antelope Valley and Golden State freeway overpasses. I 
watched the progress daily, and their efforts are to be commended, especially 
through the rain and heat. It is a job quickly well done, and I appreciate 
their making my drive to and from work easier. 
</P>
<P>
 BETSY KLEIN 
</P>
<P>
 Santa Clarita 
</P>
