<HEADLINE>
<P>
WORLD CUP USA 1994; SPOTLIGHT; THINK SO? WELL. . . 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By JOHAN CRUYFF, Folha de Sao Paulo 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 In a guest column: 
</P>
<P>
 "If Romario does not score a goal, no one scores for Brazil. . . . He invents 
his own (plays). He is capable of transforming an imaginary goal into reality. 
He cannot be criticized, ever." JOHAN CRUYFF, Folha de Sao Paulo 
