WORLD CUP USA 1994; SPOTLIGHT; BUYERS' MARKET 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By HELENE ELLIOTT 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Tickets were available almost for the asking for the third-place game 
Saturday. 
</P>
<P>
 Would-be sellers held up traffic along Orange Grove Boulevard by stepping out 
into the street and waving tickets at drivers. 
</P>
<P>
 There didn't seem to be many takers -- but the delays caused by the sellers 
were horrendous. HELENE ELLIOTT 
</P>
