<P>
 Romario was the only Brazilian starter who did not practice Saturday.He was 
seen with an ice pack on his right thigh Friday afternoon, but the team 
physician, Lidio Toledo, said he is not injured. A Brazilian reporter said 
Romario told him he would not practice because he is tired. Asked if the other 
players resented that, the reporter said: "No. Romario is Romario." RANDY 
HARVEY 
