</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Robert Mejia Alvarado has been appointed special markets manager for Coors 
Brewing Co.'s Irvine office.He was previously an account director for 
Tracy-Locke/Ornelas in Los Angeles, where he was responsible for ethnic market 
initiatives for Pepsi-Cola. In addition, Armando Bravo was appointed retail 
account manager for the California-Hawaii Field Business Unit. He most recently 
worked as district sales manager for H&L Distributing Co. in Santa Fe Springs. 
</P>
</TEXT>
