<HEADLINE>
<P>
OBITUARIES 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Moore, Darrell Lee, 45, of Moorpark, designer. Guardian Memorial Funeral 
Directors, Oxnard. 
</P>
<P>
 Rogers Diane, 49, of Port Hueneme, homemaker. Guardian Memorial Funeral 
Directors, Oxnard. 
</P>
<P>
 Sanchez, Fidel Victor, 70, of Oxnard, a retired citrus associate manager. 
James A. Reardon Mortuary, Oxnard. 
</P>
<P>
 Wolford, Elmer Donald, 69, of Ventura, retired from the U. S. military. 
Guardian Memorial Funeral Directors, Oxnard. 
</P>
<P>
 Ventura County obituaries are published free of charge as a public service to 
readers. Obituaries are based on information provided by mortuaries. 
