<HEADLINE>
<P>
THE NEXT LOS ANGELES / TURNING IDEAS INTO ACTION; LIVABLE L.A.; HOW CAN WE 
GUILD A SENSE OF COMMUNITY AND IMPROVE THE QUALITY OF LIFE AWAY FROM JOB, 
FREEWAY AND POLICE STATION?; THE TIMES POLL: HOW TO IMPROVE LIFE IN L.A. 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
